text:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

beta = 626.2
delta = 600
ro = 0.2

dt = 0.1

def Ni_pl_1(Ni):
    return dt*(beta*(Ni**2)/(1+Ni) - delta*Ni - ro*(Ni**2)) + Ni

N = [0.001]

t = np.arange(0, 1, dt)

for i in t[1:]:
    print(N[-1])
    N.append(Ni_pl_1(N[-1]))

plt.plot(t, N)
